queries.sql: SELECT `job_title`, `total_pending_applicants`, `id` FROM `job_posts` LEFT JOIN (SELECT COUNT(id) AS total_pending_applicants, job_post_id FROM job_applications WHERE application_status=0 GROUP BY job_post_id) AS job_applications ON `job_applications`.`job_post_id` = `job_posts`.`id` WHERE `is_deleted` = 0 AND `total_pending_applicants` > 0
